description:
This is a 22 minute workout called '22 Minute Full Body Gentle Yoga Practice for Beginners and Athletes' from the channel Breathe and Flow.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This is a 22 minute full body gentle yoga practice for beginners. Ideal for athletes and easy days to recover, stretch and strengthen.
